class Hike {
    constructor(
        id, 
        date, 
        time,
        mountain,
        route,
        pace,
        aboutDetails,
        gasSplit,
        host,
        attendees,
        currentWeather
        ){
            this.id = id,
            this.date= date,
            this.time= time,
            this.mountain= mountain,
            this.route = route,
            this.pace = pace,
            this.aboutDetails = aboutDetails,
            this.gasSplit = gasSplit,
            this.host = host,
            this.attendees = attendees,
            this.currentWeather = currentWeather
    }
}

export default Hike
